All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AccountController
The AccountController class manages the account page functionality and user interface events in the Enigma application.
AsciiCipher
The AsciiCipher class extends the AsciiParent class and provides an implementation for performing the ASCII cipher operation on a given cipher text.
AsciiDeCipher
The AsciiDeCipher class extends the AsciiParent class and provides an implementation for deciphering a given cipher text using ASCII cipher.
AsciiParent
The AsciiParent class is an abstract class that provides a template for performing ASCII cipher operations.
Cipher
The Cipher class represents a multi-level cipher that combines different cipher techniques to encode a text.
CipherController
The `CipherController` class handles the encryption functionality and manages the cipher page.
CopyPaste
The CopyPaste class is responsible for managing the copy and paste functionality in the application.
DeCipher
The DeCipher class represents a multi-level decipher that reverses the ciphering operations performed by the Cipher class.
DeCipherController
The `DeCipherController` class handles the decryption functionality and manages the decipher page.
FileManager
The FileManager class provides methods to read from and write to a CSV file.
IChangeable
The IChangeable interface represents the capability to modify a list of CSV records.
IEncodable
The IEncodable interface defines the contract for objects that can perform ciphering operations.
ITimer
The ITimer interface represents a timer functionality with two methods: duringTimer and afterTimer.
KeysPageController
The `KeysPageController` class is responsible for managing the keys page and related operations.
LogInController
The LogInController class handles the login functionality and user interface events related to login, signup, and user actions in the Enigma application.
LogInLogic
The LogInLogic class handles the logic for user login authentication.
Main
 
MainPageController
The MainPageController class manages the main page functionality and user interface events in the Enigma application.
ModifyFiles
The ModifyFiles class provides methods to modify CSV files.
PaneManager
The PaneManager class is responsible for managing the navigation between different panes in the application.
SecretCode
The SecretCode class represents the change of secret code functionality in the Enigma application.
ShiftCipher
The ShiftCipher class is a concrete implementation of the ShiftParent class.
ShiftDeCipher
The ShiftDeCipher class is a concrete implementation of the ShiftParent class.
ShiftParent
The ShiftParent class is an abstract class that defines the structure for a shift cipher algorithm.
SignUpController
The SignUpController class handles the signup functionality and user interface events related to user registration in the Enigma application.
SignUpLogic
The SignUpLogic class handles the logic for user sign-up process.
SubstituteCipher
The SubstituteCipher class is responsible for performing the ciphering operation using a substitution cipher.
SubstituteDeCipher
The SubstituteDeCipher class is responsible for performing the deciphering operation using a substitution cipher.
SubstituteParent
The SubstituteParent class is a parent class for substitution ciphers.
TextValidator
The TextValidator class is responsible for validating the input text and key before encryption or decryption.
Timer
The Timer class provides a simple way to execute code with a specified time delay.
Trophy
The Trophy class represents the trophies earned by a user in the Enigma application.
TrophyController
The controller class for the TrophyPage.
User
The User class represents a user in the Enigma application.
